# UIWebView和WKWebview的实现网页轻轻的方法

## UIWebView

```Swift
 myWebView.load(URLRequest(url:URL(string:"https://www.pptv.com")!))
```
参考链接：[How To Create A WebView Browser In Xcode 8 (Swift 3)](https://youtu.be/IzNJfMzjOkQ)

## WKWebView

```Swift
 override func viewDidLoad() {
        super.viewDidLoad()
       
        let url:URL = URL(string:"https://www.google.com")!//设置网址
        let Request:URLRequest = URLRequest(url:url)//根据URL进行网络请求
        
        myWebView.load(Request)//载入网页
    }
```
参考链接：[WebKit webviewbrowser - iOS Development in Swift 4-09)](https://youtu.be/xQmZSKxOYvs)
        
